<emphasis id="B58DEA94B0398807FF0FF93B9BCC72E6" bold="true" box="[174,403,1711,1738]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="478">Oesophagostomum</emphasis>
sp.
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="87463686B0398807FF42F95B996E72C6" blockId="7.[174,1233,1487,1802]" box="[227,817,1743,1770]" pageId="7" pageNumber="478">Hosts: common eland (P = 28.9 %; I = 9.7 (1–29)).</paragraph>
<paragraph id="87463686B0398807FF42F97B98547326" blockId="7.[174,1233,1487,1802]" box="[227,523,1775,1802]" pageId="7" pageNumber="478">Site of infection: caecum.</paragraph>
